What they actually want to hear

For Open Banking, success is not just:

“we shipped APIs”
“we wrote OKRs”

It is measured across 4 dimensions:

1. Customer trust & control

Because this is a regulated data-sharing product

2. Ecosystem adoption

Are FinTechs actually using it?

3. Platform reliability & security

Is it safe and stable at scale?

4. Developer experience (critical for API platforms)

Is integration easy or painful?
